Be informed, ITHM Tamaraws!  

Pubmat by: Alexi Margarette Montecastro

Reference: https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1F6jZ9Zqi5/?mibextid=wwXIfr

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 Membership Applications]

📢 𝗖𝗔𝗟𝗟𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗔𝗦𝗣𝗜𝗥𝗔𝗡𝗧𝗦! 📢

Ready to step up, show up, and stand out? Whether you perform on stage, capture stories through media, or create designs that inspire — this is your moment to join the movement.

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐬 (𝐏𝐞𝐫𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬): 
🗓 September 15–17 | ⏰ 6:00–8:30 PM

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐬 (𝐍𝐨𝐧-𝐏𝐞𝐫𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬):
🗓 September 10-16 | ⏰ Forms open until 11:59 PM

Click the link below to register:
https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 Stay tuned for the official guidelines and instructions. Keep your eyes open — 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘤𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘥𝘳𝘰𝘱𝘴 𝘴𝘰𝘰𝘯.

Hisami Muramatsu
